				<div class="postbody">
				Look for a scratch n dent type of place. Or a place that gets the overstock from Sears etc. We got a very nice washer, dryer and kickass fridge for 1k. We can upgrade on the washer because there was a ding..extremely small ding on the back of our fridge. Pretty much half of what you'd spend in the store.
<br />

<br />
We bought our stuff at Appliance Direct, but most cities have places like it.<br />
				<span class="gensmall"></span><br />
				</div>
