				<div class="postbody">
				Don't ever put it on a Sears card!  <img src="images/smiles/banghead.gif" alt="banghead" border="0" /> 
<br />
However, most Sears stores have a Clearance room with Merch that was damaged in the back room or in transit, some was purchased and returned.  In the 3 years I worked for those demons I saw some amazing deals back there.   Think like car buying, buy just slightly used and save a bundle.
<br />

